Personalised experience¬

Guest associates have a direct line to the customer, with visibility into how customers respond to products, how merchandising is working, and the effectiveness of guest promotions. Arm your front-line staff and management with the information to quickly respond to customer needs and improve service.
The right products & services

Offer the right product, in the right place, at the right time with predictive analytics. Microsoft and our partners arm you with solutions to help cost-effectively manage inventory and make sure the right products are in the right locations to optimise the customer experience through predictive analytics.
Faster decision making¬

The amount of data that can be collected to make better business decisions is exploding. But without the right tools to sift, visualise, and interpret that data into actionable insight, the flood of information can paralyse decision-making. Microsoft’s complete platform approach to business intelligence includes data management, analytics, and vertical integration to familiar Office productivity applications, enabling self-service access for users across the organisation.
